Test that source files carry SPDX headers

Adds rumpelpod/tests/license_headers.rs, sitting alongside the
THIRD-PARTY-NOTICES check and serving the same purpose: it walks
every tracked .rs/.sh/.toml/.yml file and Dockerfile and fails if
the SPDX copyright and Apache-2.0 license lines are missing from
the top, so a new source file cannot be merged without attribution.
